public static enum DateTimeFormat.PredefinedFormat extends Enum<DateTimeFormat.PredefinedFormat>
Predefined date/time formats -- see CustomDateTimeFormat if you need some format that isn't supplied here. deprecated use DateTimeFormat.PredefinedFormat instead
